e curve<br />\n<a href=\"https://corsair.com/corsairmedia/sys_master/productcontent/RMx_Manual.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcorsair.com%2Fcorsairmedia%2Fsys_master%2Fproductcontent%2FRMx_Manual.pdf&d=RH6Ab9G4Smx3Ukb%2FUx9OAG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=9526ae7b\" target=\"_blank\">https://corsair.com/corsairmedia/sys_master/productcontent/RMx_Manual.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n唔建議買1000W或以上既火牛，因為咁樣就要用具超過5A fuse既電源線，同埋嗰啲火牛太長喇"},{"pid":"834bc6123cfa61b822ea7cf7eabe507ff386774e","tid":999550,"uid":227089,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T08:02:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"68d0cb3a5aa70fc6675b757d92aba5f45d4dc328","tid":999550,"uid":49812,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"834bc6123cfa61b822ea7cf7eabe507ff386774e","tid":999550,"uid":227089,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"6a40a4f1d9a7bd6d508d78ebc44f1e9f12694c36","tid":999550,"uid":49812,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"cc579c0a39112b5256294769fc7bd3d3832aec75","tid":999550,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T03:28:14.000Z","msg":"850w真係唔上唔落, 單卡又唔洗咁大, sli又唔夠力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T07:12:21.000Z","msg":"點解寧願用850W火牛？<br />\n<br />\n零轉速風扇模式<br />\n因為只在需要時才啟動風扇，所以您將體驗到低負載和中等負載下的近乎無聲運行。<br />\n低至中負載係指40%或以下負載<br />\n<br />\n留意吓pdf檔內softcopy第4~8頁既fan noise curve<br />\n<a href=\"https://corsair.com/corsairmedia/sys_master/productcontent/RMx_Manual.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcorsair.com%2Fcorsairmedia%2Fsys_master%2Fproductcontent%2FRMx_Manual.pdf&d=RH6Ab9G4Smx3Ukb%2FUx9OAG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=9526ae7b\" target=\"_blank\">https://corsair.com/corsairmedia/sys_master/productcontent/RMx_Manual.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n唔建議買1000W或以上既火牛，因為咁樣就要用具超過5A fuse既電源線，同埋嗰啲火牛太長喇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T08:02:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T08:10:17.000Z","msg":"下置牛既風扇係應該都要向下擺架！<br />\n如果你將下置牛既風扇向上擺，就係擺錯，因為火牛既風扇係向其內部吹架<br />\n<br />\n顯示卡既風扇係無火牛既風扇咁嘈"},{"pid":"ef915132e750fdef194dacdcbc8c7ca077cd24a1","tid":999550,"uid":33176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T08:21:04.000Z","msg":"食電壞腎＋食電域加都食咗500幾W <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fe8e03d9c20bc2f1f92d5d2170b1d216c2847df","tid":999550,"uid":227089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T08:29:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a30ecdefde3288f9653b43e6628aa8c101640a4e","tid":999550,"uid":49812,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"8fe8e03d9c20bc2f1f92d5d2170b1d216c2847df","tid":999550,"uid":227089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"68d0cb3a5aa70fc6675b757d92aba5f45d4dc328","tid":999550,"uid":49812,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"834bc6123cfa61b822ea7cf7eabe507ff386774e","tid":999550,"uid":227089,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T08:02:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T08:10:17.000Z","msg":"下置牛既風扇係應該都要向下擺架！<br />\n如果你將下置牛既風扇向上擺，就係擺錯，因為火牛既風扇係向其內部吹架<br />\n<br />\n顯示卡既風扇係無火牛既風扇咁嘈"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T08:29:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T08:58:50.000Z","msg":"你無睇清楚，我只好重覆<br />\n<br />\n下置牛既風扇係應該都要向下擺架！<br />\n如果你將下置牛既風扇向上擺，就係擺錯，因為火牛既風扇係向<span style=\"color: red;\">其內部</span>吹架<br />\n<br />\n顯示卡既風扇係無火牛既風扇咁嘈"},{"pid":"639c4b89247e8829d030e6cee9feb58d60c8e7c1","tid":999550,"uid":49812,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T09:12:02.000Z","msg":"仲有，火牛既風扇經長期啟動後會變得有雜音，但係無得拆架<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/864702\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/864702</a><br />\n（#647）<br />\n隻SilverStone ST60F-P全模組火牛而家當後備，因為大手買入咗Corsair全模組火牛&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n顯示卡既生命週期（唔係指易壞程度，睇清楚）係比火牛短，未聽過啲人成日換火牛，除咗我。啲人追顯示卡就有，我感到啞子吃黃蓮！<br />\n<br />\n我換咗成個機箱，點會唔知？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/963191\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/963191</a><br />\n（#6）<br />\n本來用Cooler Master ATX鋁機箱，但之後改用Lian Li PC-A04 Micro-ATX鋁機箱。因為後者的火牛位在下方，可以減低噪音；而且後者的上方、硬碟位、前面板可拆除，便於安裝。我已丢掉前者"},{"pid":"202b7ac98ea0a92d0c3a7a15bf86e8b1fa960ec1","tid":999550,"uid":49812,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T09:13:11.000Z","msg":"仲有，火牛既風扇經長期啟動後會變得有雜音，但係無得拆架<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/864702/page/26\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/864702/page/26</a><br />\n（#647）<br />\n隻SilverStone ST60F-P全模組火牛而家當後備，因為大手買入咗Corsair全模組火牛&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n顯示卡既生命週期（唔係指易壞程度，睇清楚）係比火牛短，未聽過啲人成日換火牛，除咗我。啲人追顯示卡就有，我感到啞子吃黃蓮！<br />\n<br />\n我換咗成個機箱，點會唔知？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/963191\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/963191</a><br />\n（#6）<br />\n本來用Cooler Master ATX鋁機箱，但之後改用Lian Li PC-A04 Micro-ATX鋁機箱。因為後者的火牛位在下方，可以減低噪音；而且後者的上方、硬碟位、前面板可拆除，便於安裝。我已丢掉前者"},{"pid":"e654656560db817c43d570457aff7173a192425c","tid":999550,"uid":227089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T10:05:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ddeeb01ea1a903a775abc4a199a4b6aa2b0c767d","tid":999550,"uid":227089,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T10:16:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3096f8592606d76ed77370b44b016ca36c1eb399","tid":999550,"uid":49812,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ddeeb01ea1a903a775abc4a199a4b6aa2b0c767d","tid":999550,"uid":227089,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"639c4b89247e8829d030e6cee9feb58d60c8e7c1","tid":999550,"uid":49812,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T09:12:02.000Z","msg":"仲有，火牛既風扇經長期啟動後會變得有雜音，但係無得拆架<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/864702\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/864702</a><br />\n（#647）<br />\n隻SilverStone ST60F-P全模組火牛而家當後備，因為大手買入咗Corsair全模組火牛&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n顯示卡既生命週期（唔係指易壞程度，睇清楚）係比火牛短，未聽過啲人成日換火牛，除咗我。啲人追顯示卡就有，我感到啞子吃黃蓮！<br />\n<br />\n我換咗成個機箱，點會唔知